summary: Here’s the thing. I think in the books Arya travels, but i also think she settles down eventually. She names her wolf after...
body:
Here’s the thing. I think in the books Arya travels, but i also think she settles down eventually. She names her wolf after Nymeria who lead her people to Dorne and married the prince there so her people will be safe. 

“We are in part, Your Grace. Nymeria’s blood is in me, along with that of Mors Martell, the Dornish lord she married. On the day they wed, Nymeria fired her ships, so her people would understand that there could be no going back. Most were glad to see those flames, for their voyagings had been long and terrible before they came to Dorne, and many and more had been lost to storm, disease, and slavery. There were a few who mourned, however. They did not love this dry red land or its seven-faced god, so they clung to their old ways, hammered boats together from the hulks of the burned ships, and became the orphans of the Greenblood. The Mother in their songs is not our Mother, but Mother Rhoyne, whose waters nourished them from the dawn of days.“ - the Queenmaker 

Arya, herself, is named after Arya Flint of the Mountain Clans. Arya Flint wed Rodrik Stark who was known as the Wandering Wolf. 

She is surrounded by travelers, thats true. But she is also surrounded by travelers who came home or somewhere else and settled there.

title: AU! Game of interaction
body:
I will post some of my thoughts about Westeros women interaction, because I like when women are friends, rather than some enemies, also why not? (some of them already had meet in tv show, but I don’t liked, sorry not sorry)

Part one: Arya Stark and Daenerys Targaryen 

Arya’s heart stop when she see a dragon who fly above her, a real one. She know very well that dragons are dead, but she trust her own eyes. Arya watch how he fly, when she see there is someone on dragon. Silver hair was so recognizable, that she understand that is not anyone but Daenerys Targaryen. They have not yet meet, but Arya was saw her when she arrived with Jon.

Later she saw they landed to the ground. Young Stark was fascinated by how gracious the dragon wing stretched to let Daenerys to get down from him. Such a simple move, but it shows how strong is bounding between Targaryen’s and dragon’s.

- He is beautiful, say Arya when Dragons Queen approached her.

- Yes he is, say Dany with a proud smile

- What’s his name?

- Drogon, he is fierce as person I named him after.

- It’s a dragon’s like name, I’m Arya Stark.

- I recognize now a Stark when I see one.

- Well, there is not left much of us, so you shouldn’t faced a problem with that.

- You have a sister and two brothers, i have only my dragons. I’m the last Targaryen in world.

- I hear dragons live longer than us

- They will carry my legacy, she said with a smile. You look so much like Jon, you know after he meet you something change in his eyes.

- What?

- They faded away a lot of sadness.

- Did you know something about Visenya Targaryen?
